    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>
Here's an example of my unreasonably long pipeline from MakeHuman to
skeletal animation with Haxe. The left and right arrow keys change
the blending weight between idle and speed-walking animations. Hovering
demostrates the IK blend node which is operating on the right arm.
You may need to click on the flash player to give it focus.
</p>


